news.title: Revenue authorities cite hurdles to execute MahaRERA orders
news.para: With nearly 751 recovery warrant orders to be executed, the authorities are facing issues with carrying out the orders and ensuring that homebuyers receive their invested money back.

news.title: NBCC Green View buyers write to housing minister, seek rent relief extension
news.para: By July, NBCC had put forward its first compensation package to the homebuyers, saying that it will refund their original purchase amounts - in the range of Rs 65 lakh to Rs 1.5 crore - along with the sum spent on registry.

news.title: Gurugram: Three builders fail to clear audit dues, may face action
news.para: "These three developers were directed to deposit the structural audit fees latest by Monday evening. However, none of them has complied with the directions," Gurugram's deputy commissioner Nishant Yadav said on Tuesday.
